Please install Sherpa before you use it: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1GEEsM-2HavQ2EUgNfMGFneEUDNehUjE3FqOiGa5pRSQ/edit

    1.Clone the git and copy the Run.dat file to your Sherpa/bin
    $ git clone ...
    $ cd /.../QCD-event-Pythia-Herwig-Sherpa
    $ cp ./Run.dat /home/yourname/SHERPA-MC-2.2.9 /Sherpa/bin
    
    2.Modify the file Run.dat line 20 : "EVT_FILE_PATH=/home/ja2006203966/event/Sherpa/" to the path you want output
    the hepmc2 file
    
    3.Go th your /Sherpa/bin
     $ cd /.../Sherpa/bin
     $  ./Sherpa PATH=/.../Sherpa/bin -e 100
     
  See more information: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1c171KOhQ3X55oj6fUaHHVsoBSezL2WSW

